Package de.db.derpate.persistence

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Dao<K,​E>
    Interface each data access object should implement, including methods to find an entry by id, list all entities, persist/update/remove an entity.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminDao
    Data Access Object providing methods to get Admin objects out of the Database
    EmailPasswordLoginUserDao<K,​E>
    Abstract Data Access Object, that can be used for all objects, that extend EmailPasswordLoginUser, to get their id, email and password
    EntityManagerFactory
    This factory uses java's Persistence class to create an EntityManagerFactory and EntityManager's using the persistence settings file (src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml).
    Pattern: Singleton
    GodfatherDao
    Data Access Object providing methods to get Godfather objects out of the Database
    IdDao<K,​E>
    Data Access Object, that can be used for all models, that extend from Id
    JobDao
    Data Access Object providing methods to get Jobs out of the Database
    LocationDao
    Data Access Object object providing methods to get Locations out of the Database
    TeachingTypeDao
    Data Access Object providing methods to get TeachingTypes out of the Database
    TraineeDao
    Data Access Object providing methods to get Trainees out of the Database
